News.title: New 1
News.Description: Voith sets standards in the markets energy, oil & gas, paper, raw materials and transport & automotive. Founded in 1867, Voith employs more than 20,000 people, generates € 4.3 billion in sales, operates in about 60 countries around the world and is today one of the largest family-owned companies in Europe*.
